argument.name: run_dir
argument.description: Relative path of the run directory.

argument.name: api_key
argument.description: Call the API and pull JSON tariff file(s) with EIA ID corresponding to the EPW region.

argument.name: tariff_directory
argument.description: Absolute (or relative) directory to tariff files.

argument.name: tariff_file_name
argument.description: Name of the JSON tariff file. Leave blank if pulling JSON tariff file(s) with EIA ID corresponding to the EPW region.

argument.name: ng_fixed
argument.description: Annual fixed cost of natural gas.

argument.name: ng_rate
argument.description: Price per therm for natural gas.

argument.name: oil_rate
argument.description: Price per gallon for fuel oil.

argument.name: avg_rates
argument.description: Average across residential rates in a given EIA ID.
